Package: ggbipartite
Type: Package
Title: Visualize Bipartite Networks with ggplot2
Version: 0.9.2
Authors@R: c(
    person("Hidehito", "Okada", , "hidefungi@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-3210-2736"))
  )
Description: Provides tools to visualize bipartite interaction matrices on
    of ggplot2. It includes stat/geom layers to draw row and column
    boxes and interaction polygons, coordinate constructors for custom
    workflows, and helpers to align bipartite layouts with phylogenetic
    trees.
